body.content:
Go to your OneDrive | View it online
Welcome to your OneDrive
OneDrive is your personal cloud storage that keeps your files protected, backed up, and accessible across your devices. It comes with 5 GB of free storage and you can always purchase more storage with a paid subscription.
Go to your OneDrive
Access your files from
anywhere
You can back up any file or photo on your computer and access them from the OneDrive app on your phone or tablet or web browser. Get OneDrive
Protect your most important documents
Use Personal Vault to securely store your sensitive documents (passport, driver's license) with your fingerprint, face, PIN or a code. Learn More
Back up PC folders
Automatically back up your Desktop, Documents and Pictures folders, so you always have your files even if your PC is lost or stolen. Learn More
Easily share files
Share links to your photos and files with anyone and choose whether they can only view or edit.
Get 1 TB and more out of OneDrive by upgrading to Office 365
Premium OneDrive features
1 TB = 300,000 photos plus files*
30-Day File Backup & Restore
Ransomware Detection & Recovery
Newest Office apps for PC & Mac
Go premium
*Assumes photos are 4MB JPGs and documents are 0.8MB Office files.
This email was sent from an unmonitored mailbox.

You are receiving this message because you have a Microsoft OneDrive account.
Copyright 2020 Microsoft Corporation.
Privacy Statement
